HEADWORD: jangly
<hw>jangly</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>like the discordant ringing of
nonmusical metallic objects striking together; sounding with a
jangle{3}; <as>as, a custodian with a <ex>jangly</ex> set of
keys</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> jangling.</syn>⟦br⟧
